sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Free User
    participant FE as React<br/>SubscriptionPage
    participant API as DRF<br/>UpgradeSubscriptionView
    participant SER as UpgradeSubscriptionSerializer
    participant Stripe as Stripe API
    participant Router as TierDatabaseRouter
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>FE: Select target tier, click "Upgrade"
    FE->>API: POST /api/subscriptions/upgrade/ {plan: "premium"}
    API->>SER: UpgradeSubscriptionSerializer.validate(data)
    SER-->>API: Validated plan selection
    API->>Stripe: stripe.PaymentIntent.create(amount, currency)
    Stripe-->>API: Payment confirmed
    API->>Router: set_db_for_role("premium")
    API->>DB: Migrate user data to premium_db
    API->>DB: UserSubscription.objects.update(plan="premium")
    DB-->>API: Subscription updated
    API-->>FE: 200 OK {new_plan, features}
    FE-->>U: Display "Upgrade successful" with new features
